Shotgun,is,a,service,for,creative,studios,Shotgun,provides,pipeline,tools,for,studios,and,creative,processes,Features,include,schedules,tracking,reviewing,and,collaboration,The,Shotgun,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,Shotgun,with,other,applications,Some,example,API,methods,include,retrieving,schedules,managing,tasks,and,managing,account,information